#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/loadlayer.rst:41
msgid ""
"Let's open some layers with data. QGIS recognizes vector and raster layers. "
"Additionally, custom layer types are available, but we are not going to "
"discuss them here."
msgstr "我們來開啟一些有資料的圖層。QGIS 可辨識向量和網格影像圖層。除此之外，也可以開啟自定的圖層類型，但是我們這裡並不打算討論它們。"

#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/loadlayer.rst:49
msgid "Vector Layers"
msgstr "向量圖層"

#: ../../docs/pyqgis_developer_cookbook/loadlayer.rst:282
